four different isotopes.

327
00:15:08,325 --> 00:15:08,950
Actually, wait.

328
00:15:08,950 --> 00:15:12,580
Let me put all the other junk
in front to make it quicker.

329
00:15:12,580 --> 00:15:16,625
So the 4 pi k0 squared
little z squared

330
00:15:16,625 --> 00:15:22,180
e to the fourth
over MeV squared is

331
00:15:22,180 --> 00:15:31,710
just a constant, times the
sum over all your isotopes

332
00:15:31,710 --> 00:15:37,560
of zi, the number
density of isotope i,

333
00:15:37,560 --> 00:15:43,250
which inside there has the
element fraction of that,

334
00:15:43,250 --> 00:15:48,600
times the log of 2 MeV squared
over the mean ionization

335
00:15:48,600 --> 00:15:52,446
potential of isotope i.

336
00:15:52,446 --> 00:15:55,378
And in this case, notice
