346
00:16:18,140 --> 00:16:20,840
Carbon is just carbon-12,
except for the tiny amount

347
00:16:20,840 --> 00:16:23,630
of carbon-14 you use
for radio carbon dating.

348
00:16:23,630 --> 00:16:27,530
Oxygen, it's oxygen--
think what, 16?

349
00:16:27,530 --> 00:16:29,510
Nitrogen is nitrogen-14.

350
00:16:29,510 --> 00:16:31,580
So as long as you know
